  "texts": [
    "Information about how they can do so should be available.",
    "In cases when someone requests withdrawal of their name from use, the name can no longer be used for future publications.",
    "However, the GDPR also allows for a request for data erasure.",
    "In these cases, the name should, if reasonably possible, also be removed from past publications.",
    "When doing so, it should be asked if deleting the name prevents the achievement of the goals of the publication and/or research."
  ],
